### Delivery

> Putting delivery section on top for a clear status, see proposal below.

https://github.com/prometheus/prometheus/pull/17610 is the "preview" PR with all changes so far. Once buildable, we can prombench and see the effects (e.g. import from downstream code).

#### M1

* [x] *PART1*: Add `AppenderV2` interface; add TSDB implementation (next to `Appender`): https://github.com/prometheus/prometheus/pull/17629
* [x]  *PART2*: Refactor scrape package; add adapters for multi version of Appender use: https://github.com/prometheus/prometheus/pull/17631
* [x]  *PART3*: Add `AppenderV2` interface to TSDB Agent https://github.com/prometheus/prometheus/pull/17677
* [x]  *PART4*: Switch OTLP, RW receiving: 
